Pandora Enhancer is an extension that adds more functionality to Pandora's awesome new HTML5 interface.

It is currently available on the Chrome Web Store at https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ipfamfogncacknldkaoekchdeddmfnlg?hl=en

